Small project istanbul challenge is finding or creqting a measurement tool. The solution is already there where you can implement Power BI to the project. For small projects, it is free and can do all the tasks and measurements, evaluation and performace process within some clicks also all data can be visulaized.  In this video, it shows you how it works: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r5bhvXAsDFk. Hopefully this tool will be as helpful as posible. 
